
## üìä Monthly Sales Trend Analysis with SQLite

### üìù Objective:

Analyze online sales data to identify monthly revenue trends and order volumes for performance monitoring and business insights.

---

### üìÇ Dataset: `online_sales`

| Column Name | Type     | Description                         |
| ----------- | -------- | ----------------------------------- |
| order\_id   | TEXT/INT | Unique ID of the order              |
| order\_date | DATE     | Date when the order was placed      |
| amount      | FLOAT    | Total amount of the order in INR/\$ |

---

### üìå Key Analyses:

#### üÖ∞Ô∏è Extract Month from Order Date

```sql
SELECT
    EXTRACT(MONTH FROM order_date) AS month
FROM
    online_sales;
```

#### üÖ±Ô∏è Extract Year from Order Date

```sql
SELECT
    EXTRACT(YEAR FROM order_date) AS year
FROM
    online_sales;
```

#### üÖ≤ Group Data by Year and Month

```sql
SELECT
    EXTRACT(YEAR FROM order_date) AS year,
    EXTRACT(MONTH FROM order_date) AS month
FROM
    online_sales
GROUP BY
    EXTRACT(YEAR FROM order_date),
    EXTRACT(MONTH FROM order_date);
```

#### üÖ≥ Calculate Total Revenue per Month

```sql
SELECT
    EXTRACT(YEAR FROM order_date) AS year,
    EXTRACT(MONTH FROM order_date) AS month,
    SUM(amount) AS total_revenue
FROM
    online_sales
GROUP BY
    year, month;
```

#### üÖ¥ Calculate Distinct Order Volume per Month

```sql
SELECT
    EXTRACT(YEAR FROM order_date) AS year,
    EXTRACT(MONTH FROM order_date) AS month,
    COUNT(DISTINCT order_id) AS order_volume
FROM
    online_sales
GROUP BY
    year, month;
```

#### üÖµ Full Monthly Sales Trend Query

```sql
SELECT
    EXTRACT(YEAR FROM order_date) AS year,
    EXTRACT(MONTH FROM order_date) AS month,
    SUM(amount) AS total_revenue,
    COUNT(DISTINCT order_id) AS order_volume
FROM
    online_sales
GROUP BY
    year, month
ORDER BY
    year, month;
```

#### üÖ∂ Filter Results for Year 2024

```sql
SELECT
    EXTRACT(YEAR FROM order_date) AS year,
    EXTRACT(MONTH FROM order_date) AS month,
    SUM(amount) AS total_revenue,
    COUNT(DISTINCT order_id) AS order_volume
FROM
    online_sales
WHERE
    EXTRACT(YEAR FROM order_date) = 2024
GROUP BY
    year, month
ORDER BY
    year, month;
``
